fitnesse.fixtures

SetUp

A page may not be renamed to a name with dots in it.

Another way of saying this is that renaming a page does not change it's position.


First build the page to rename, and another page to try to move it beneath.

Page creator.
Page name. Page contents. valid?
MyPage X true
TargetPage X true

Then rename that page.

Response Requester.
uri status?
MyPage?responder=renamePage&newName=TargetPage.SomePage 400

Make sure that we got an error message.

Response Examiner.
type pattern matches? wrapped html?
contents Cannot rename true
